Metadata.Title: Gang Virus
Metadata.Description: In this contract you need to kill these members of a Gang known as FNF Since the gang is infected with a deadly disease and plan on infecting Sapienzia with a virus called FNF. You will  need to go long ranged with a sniper so you do not get infected with the FNF Virus. we will sneak you in as mansion security. Also note that the plan is in final stages and the targets are most likely very close to leaving the town to infect more locations so you may only have very little time to engage.
